  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001310/extras/75834940535e54d82bbb793c36cb22d0.poster.avif?t=1770805443\" width=400 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001310/extras/75834940535e54d82bbb793c36cb22d0.webm?t=1770805443\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001310/extras/75834940535e54d82bbb793c36cb22d0.mp4?t=1770805443\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Farming & Building</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Grow crops and gather gold to build essential buildings for your adventurers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Build facilities to hire adventurers and customize your guild.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001310/extras/c0359544510eafc06809a8c66403dba1.avif?t=1770805443\" width=400 height=100 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Research</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Discover and unlock over 100 unique objects to optimize and expand your guild.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001310/extras/882c52f910c4145fbd8342e591aa2ef7.avif?t=1770805443\" width=400 height=100 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Hire Adventurers</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Hire adventurers and manage your growing guild.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Assign them to a variety of tasks including monster hunting, mining, cooking, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001310/extras/a8837f6267ba5ea47584e61ef0334be8.avif?t=1770805443\" width=400 height=100 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Corrupted Liquid</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Monsters generate Corrupted Liquid, which can attract even more powerful threats.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Eliminate them before the corruption spreads too far.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001310/extras/a5e4bb0ec114bbdfee88b81b2eea28fe.poster.avif?t=1770805443\" width=400 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001310/extras/a5e4bb0ec114bbdfee88b81b2eea28fe.webm?t=1770805443\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001310/extras/a5e4bb0ec114bbdfee88b81b2eea28fe.mp4?t=1770805443\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001310/extras/66abd6d39416c238d39b2fcc3fa2e2a0.poster.avif?t=1770805443\" width=400 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001310/extras/66abd6d39416c238d39b2fcc3fa2e2a0.webm?t=1770805443\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001310/extras/66abd6d39416c238d39b2fcc3fa2e2a0.mp4?t=1770805443\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Explore the World & Underground</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Travel to distant regions and delve into the depths to uncover rare and valuable treasures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001310/extras/fda4fdd652233da6c1c6d2cbc00df664.poster.avif?t=1770805443\" width=400 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001310/extras/fda4fdd652233da6c1c6d2cbc00df664.webm?t=1770805443\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001310/extras/fda4fdd652233da6c1c6d2cbc00df664.mp4?t=1770805443\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Multiplayer Fun</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Team up with up to four friends and enjoy the full experience together online.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Cooperate on farming, building, combat, and adventurer management — everything’s better with friends!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001310/extras/5ad32d1f1b5c0bdc6a1edb754e5de2d5.poster.avif?t=1770805443\" width=400 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001310/extras/5ad32d1f1b5c0bdc6a1edb754e5de2d5.webm?t=1770805443\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001310/extras/5ad32d1f1b5c0bdc6a1edb754e5de2d5.mp4?t=1770805443\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001310/extras/45faf3733eb3c7b837276438a9bb7c29.poster.avif?t=1770805443\" width=400 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001310/extras/45faf3733eb3c7b837276438a9bb7c29.webm?t=1770805443\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001310/extras/45faf3733eb3c7b837276438a9bb7c29.mp4?t=1770805443\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">And So Much More</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Automate your farming, cook delicious dishes, run your own restaurant, and uncover countless other features!</p>",
